'''António Tavares''' (yavutse 1960),  n'umwanditsi wa Porutugali na [[Angola]]  .  Ni n'umunyamakuru, umwarimu n'umunyapolitiki wo muri [[Porutugali]]. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1960 i Lobito, muri [[Angola]] .  Mu 1975, afite imyaka 15, yimukiye muri [[Porutugali]] nyuma yo gukoronizwa muri [[Afurika]]. Nyuma yize amashuri yisumbuye i Porto. Nyuma, yarangije amategeko mu ishami ry'amategeko muri kaminuza ya Coimbra . Nyuma yaje kubona impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza mu by'amategeko agenga itumanaho muri kaminuza imwe.  Amaze kurangiza amashuri, yatangiye gukora nk'umwarimu mu mashuri yisumbuye mu Ishuri ryisumbuye Domingos Rebelo (Escola Secundária Domingos Rebelo), i Ponta Delgada, nyuma mu ishuri rya Dr. Joaquim de Carvalho (Escola Secundária Dr. Joaquim de Carvalho), muri Figueira da Foz . 

Hagati aho, yinjiye muri politiki ya [[Porutigali|Porutugali]] maze aba umuyobozi muri komine ya Figueira da Foz kuva 2005 kugeza 2009, nyuma aba umuyobozi mu nzego z'umuco, imijyi n'ibidukikije kuva 2009 kugeza 2013. Kuva mu 2013 gushika 2017, Tavares ni visi perezida wa komine. 

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2013, yakiriye icyubahiro mu gihembo cya Alves Redol kubera igitabo cyitwa 'O Tempo Adormeceu sob o Sol da Tarde'. Tavares yanditse igitabo ''kizwi cyane nka Palavras que Me Deverão Guiar um Dia'' aho yari yarangije igihembo cya Leya 2013.  Ariko, muri 2015 yatsindiye igihembo cya Leya kubera igitabo ''O Coro dos Defuntos'' (Korali y'abapfuye). Yashinze kandi ikinyamakuru yo mu karere 'A Linha do Oeste' n'ikinyamakuru 'Litorais'.  

